text: I must say that i'm not a fan of regular Starbucks coffee at the stores.  I'm a coffee lover and must have one every each day.  Anyways, i thought giving this coffee a try.  I must admit, i'm not sure what they mean by "natural fusion", but it sure does taste good. It's nice and smooth with sutble taste of vanilla. I personally like bolder taste of coffee and this coffee seems more bold.
